{
  "stem": "20711.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know he did came home least once or twice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I remember definitely-- two definitely I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it could have been more because later on, I was in a boarding school, and I had no time to observe when he was home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But before I went to the boarding school, once, he came home, and I was shocked to see his new type of a uniform.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the second time he came home and there was a strict restriction of not to able to leave your town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just came home for the vacation, but if you had part of your family in an other town, you wasn't allowed to travel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was in a boarding school by then in Kosice, and my father, under-cover, he did travel with my mom to Kosice.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they rented a hotel room, and he wasn't leaving his hotel room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother picked me up at the school, and I was able to go and visit my father in that hotel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this hurt me because it was time for us to have dinner, and there was no room service those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother and I, we went downstairs to eat in a restaurant, but my father didn't came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked my mom, why doesn't he come?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when my mom told me, he's not supposed to be here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He is risking his life just to see me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can-- do you have any other recollections of any changes in your life at that particular time between 1938 and 1943?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, little by little I heard-- especially in a boarding school, I heard anti-Semitic remarks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the sooner a nun would overhear it, they would put a stop to it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
